# 🧩 1. Feature Prioritization (MoSCoW Framework)

## 🟢 MUST HAVE (Core value creation — MVP)

These features directly solve the **“I don’t know what/how to build”** problem.

---

### 1. 🎯 Project Recommendation Engine

* Personalized project suggestions
* Based on skill, interests, tech stack

**Why MUST:**
Without this, users don’t even start → zero activation.

---

### 2. 🧪 Guided Project Mode

* Task-based execution (like real dev work)
* Step-by-step but not spoon-fed

**Why MUST:**
This is the **core learning experience** (your differentiation vs LeetCode)

---

### 3. 🤖 AI Guided Assistance (Constrained)

* Hint-based support using GitHub Copilot
* Debug help, explanation (NOT full solutions)

**Why MUST:**
Prevents drop-offs during struggle phase.

---

### 4. 🧑‍💻 Basic Feedback System (AI)

* Code quality suggestions
* Error detection

**Why MUST:**
Learning requires feedback loops.

---

### 5. 📤 Project Completion + Share

* Publish project
* Basic visibility on profile

**Why MUST:**
Creates **closure + motivation**

---

## 🟡 SHOULD HAVE (Retention & engagement drivers)

---

### 6. 🌍 Community Feed (Project Discovery)

* See what others are building
* Discover ideas

**Why SHOULD:**
Drives inspiration + FOMO

---

### 7. 🔁 Peer Feedback (PR-style reviews)

* Comment on others’ code
* Upvote good solutions

**Why SHOULD:**
Simulates real-world collaboration

---

### 8. 🏆 Basic Gamification (Milestones)

* “First project shipped”
* “Bug fixed”

**Why SHOULD:**
Encourages continuation → second project

---

### 9. 📊 Skill Graph (Basic Version)

* Show projects, activity, contributions

**Why SHOULD:**
Early version of portfolio layer

---

## 🔵 COULD HAVE (Differentiation + scale)

---

### 10. 🧠 Idea Board (Problem → Solution brainstorming)

* Post problems
* Discuss approaches

---

### 11. 📓 Dev Logs (“Build in Public”)

* Daily/weekly updates

---

### 12. 🧑‍🏫 Mentor Layer

* Industry experts reviewing projects

---

### 13. ⚔️ Team-based Projects

* Collaborate like real teams

---

## 🔴 WON’T HAVE (Now)

---

### 14. 🏢 Recruiter Marketplace

* Too early without supply quality

---

### 15. 🎓 Certifications

* Weak signal vs real work
* Misaligned with product philosophy

